data.title: Automatic Tank Gauging
data.meta_description: ProGauge ATG products are made in Italy, a leading brand owned by Dover Fueling Solutions
data.text:
The Tokheim Quantium™ 430 fuel dispenser is our wide body dispenser range designed specifically for the requirements of the Asian and Middle East markets to handle a variety of fuel types. You can choose between 4 to 8 hoses with two or four active hoses, with a flow rate option of up to 130 LPM. The ‘H-type’ pump has a simple effective hanging hose system for ease of use and meets the varying regional market requirements.

The dispenser is lane orientated and can be pressure or suction.

​

Tokheim Dispenser Supports Protocol:

IFSF LON

An International Forecourt Standards Protocol

The Quantium™ 330 fuel dispenser is Tokheim’s flexible dispenser designed specifically for the requirements of the Asian and Middle East markets to handle a variety of fuel types. You can choose between one to four hoses, with two or four active hoses with a flow rate option of up to 130 lpm. The ‘H-type’ pump has a simple effective hanging hose system for ease of use and meets the varying regional market requirements.

The dispenser is lane oriented, and can be pressure or suction.

​

Tokheim Dispenser Supports Protocol:

IFSF LON

An International Forecourt Standards Protocol

The Quantium 230T dispenser is available with either one or two hoses with a flow rate option of 40lpm to 130lpm. Flexibility to choose between a hook or spring mast system will allow you to meet your specific market needs.

The dispenser is island oriented, and can be pressure or suction.

​

Tokheim Dispenser Supports Protocol:

An International Forecourt Standards Protocol
